1.Download the Employee Attrition Dataset https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/patelprashant/employee-attrition 2.Perfrom Data Preprocessing 3.Model Building using Logistic Regression and Decision Tree 4.Calculate Performance metrics

I. PERFORM DATA PREPROCESSING¶

Steps:¶

  1. import the necessary librares
  2. import the data set
  3. handling the null values (taught in pandas class)
  4. Outlier detection. if outlier present, drop it
  5. seperate dependent and independent variables
  6. encoding
  7. feature scaling
  8. splitting into training and testing set
